cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite the article and the package."
title: "emgteach: an open-source teaching platform for surface electromyography"
abstract: >-
  emgteach is a Python package that provides a unified PySide6 desktop
  application for real-time acquisition, offline analysis and MVC
  normalisation of surface EMG signals. Two interchangeable hardware
  backends are supported: BITalino over Bluetooth and Arduino RedBoard
  Plus + MyoWare 2.0 over USB serial. Output files follow the EDF+
  standard with reliable buffered writing.
